snippet.title: Saturday Night Live
snippet.description:
Welcome to the official Saturday Night Live channel on YouTube! Here you will find your favorite sketches, behind the scenes clips and web exclusives, featuring all your favorite hosts and cast members.

All seasons of Saturday Night Live are now available on Peacock, the new streaming service from NBCUniversal. Watch thousands of hours of hit movies and shows, plus daily news, sports, and pop culture updates. Stream now on Peacock: https://bit.ly/3esVzIq
